Miscellaneous Symbols & Escaping:
To print literal characters that are normally interpreted as syntax, escape them with a backslash ( \ ).
Horizontal Rule: Produced by --- , *** , or ___ on a blank line.
Line Break: Add two or more trailing spaces at the end of a sentence line, then hit Return.
Escaping Markdown elements: \*This will not be italicized\* prints out raw asterisks.